original_title: Tame Impala Live at Saturday Night
overview: Tame Impala were last night’s musical guests on “Saturday Night Live,” which was hosted by Sandra Oh. Kevin Parker and co. made their “SNL” debut by performing their latest single “Patience.” Parker shook a maraca while he and his band were bathed in colorful, psychedelic lights. Watch it go down below.
title: Tame Impala Live at Saturday Night
